// =============================================================================
// sqlite3_backup_init — selects source + destination databases for an online
// backup. Spec §7.8 — online backup.
//

// Validation rules:
//  * source and dest must be distinct sqlite3* handles
//  * source_name and dest_name default to "main"
//  * neither handle may be in auto-vacuum transition
// =============================================================================

